              </li>
              <li>
                <p>
                  Horizontally stretch by a factor of <m>\frac{3}{2}</m>.
                  <md>
                    <mrow>A:\,(-4,2) \rightarrow (-6,2)</mrow>
                    <mrow>V_1:\,(-2,4) \rightarrow (-3,4)</mrow>
                    <mrow>V_2:\,(4,4) \rightarrow (6,4)</mrow>
                    <mrow>B:\,(6,2) \rightarrow (9,2)</mrow>
                  </md>
                </p>
              </li>
              <li>
                <p>
                  Reflect across the <m>x</m>-axis.
                  <md>
                    <mrow>A:\,(-6,2) \rightarrow (-6,-2)</mrow>
                    <mrow>V_1:\,(-3,4) \rightarrow (-3,-4)</mrow>
                    <mrow>V_2:\,(6,4) \rightarrow (6,-4)</mrow>
                    <mrow>B:\,(9,2) \rightarrow (9,-2)</mrow>
